desc_short	-----								Sniper Tactical is a casual game. Disguised as a shooter, it is actually a semi real-time/turn-based lemmings type puzzle. The gameplay revolves around bringing hostages to safe-zones which in turn is done by shooting different types of enemies in correct order.							
developer									fragOut Studio								
